WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:02.000
It was aight o'clock in the morning, 

2
00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:05.100
and the red hot sun was burning bright.

3
00:00:05.100 --> 00:00:08.200
The sky was blue, and the air dry. 

4
00:00:08.200 --> 00:00:11.500
As it was already heating up.

5
00:00:11.500 --> 00:00:12.600
Just when he woke up 

6
00:00:12.600 --> 00:00:15.100
the lazy boy heard his mother call.

7
00:00:15.100 --> 00:00:17.800
"Yes... I'm awake! I'll be down soon,

8
00:00:17.800 --> 00:00:22.800
just give me one minute!" he replied.

9
00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:26.300
His pet, a black cat, was sitting near the leg of the bed. 

10
00:00:26.300 --> 00:00:30.200
As if he wanted to say: "Goodmorning".

11
00:00:30.200 --> 00:00:33.800
"I have no time to play with you now", said the boy. 

12
00:00:33.800 --> 00:00:40.200
"I need to go to the bathroom to take a shower and wash my self".

13
00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:42.900
When the little boy came downstairs for breakfast,

14
00:00:42.900 --> 00:00:46.700
his father was sitting at the table near the window.

15
00:00:46.700 --> 00:00:52.600
He was eating some food, and drinking a cup of yellow lemon tea.

16
00:00:52.600 --> 00:00:56.800
Mother was singing with her beautiful and pure voice.

17
00:00:56.800 --> 00:01:01.900
She tried not to miss out a single note.


